[I] A real-time software synthesizer based on the SoundFont 2 specifications

[T] FluidSynth is a cross-platform, real-time software synthesizer based on the
[T] Soundfont 2 specification. FluidSynth generates audio by reading and
[T] handling MIDI events from MIDI input devices by using a SoundFont.

[U] https://www.fluidsynth.org/

[A] Fluidsynth Authors
